      "releaseNotes": "What's New\n\n- Adds support for Osmo Action 6.\n\n\nWhat's Updated\n\n- Adds “HDR” Dolby Vision mode for an immersive true‑to‑life color experience; upgrade your videos to cinematic quality with one tap\n\n- Adds a “Mix” feature: when Osmo Action 6 is connected to an external microphone, you can adjust the external mic and camera body audio levels separately.\n\n- Adds a “Filter Import” feature, supporting importing LUT files from your device as local filters; elevate image quality with one tap and easily achieve cinematic visual effects.",
      "version": "2.6.4",
